Emergency Automation System
├── Sensing & Detection Layer
│   ├── IoT Sensors (Fire, Smoke, Gas, Motion)
│   ├── CCTV & Video Analytics
│   ├── Social Media & Crowd-sourced Alerts
│   └── Telemetry (Vehicle/Drone Tracking)
│
├── Data Aggregation & Preprocessing Layer
│   ├── Real-time Data Streams (MQTT, Kafka)
│   ├── Data Fusion Algorithms
│   └── Anomaly Detection Models
│
├── Decision & Intelligence Layer
│   ├── AI-based Incident Classification
│   ├── Predictive Analytics (Incident Forecasting)
│   ├── Risk Assessment Engines
│   └── Rule-based & ML-based Decision Trees
│
├── Dispatch & Resource Management Layer
│   ├── Automated Dispatch Engines
│   ├── Dynamic Resource Allocation
│   ├── Route Optimization & ETA Prediction
│   └── Inter-agency Coordination (Police, Fire, EMS)
│
├── Communication & Control Interface Layer
│   ├── Command Center Dashboards
│   ├── Operator Alert Systems
│   ├── Mobile Apps for Field Responders
│   └── Multi-Channel Messaging (SMS, Radio, Push)
│
└── Audit, Logging & Compliance Layer
    ├── Incident Logs & Reporting
    ├── Compliance Monitoring (HIPAA, GDPR, etc.)
    ├── Post-Incident Analysis Tools
    └── Continuous Improvement Feedback Loop
